                        <note rend="inline" type="source">121.5493/10–2449: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Consul General at Peiping</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Clubb</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-10-27T18:00:00-05:00">October
                                    27, 1949—6 p. m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>744. Dept is giving consideration subj matter urtel 1805 Oct 24.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
